wrapContent.value:
<cXML payloadID="${header.SAP_MessageProcessingLogID}" timestamp="${date:now:yyyy-MM-dd'T'hh:mm:ssZ}" version="1.2.060">
	<Header>
		<From>
			<Credential domain="SystemID">
				<Identity>${header.sysid}</Identity>
			</Credential>
			<Credential domain="NetworkID">
				<Identity>${header.anid}</Identity>
			</Credential>
                        <Credential domain="EndPointID">
                           <Identity>CIG</Identity>
                    </Credential>
		</From>
		<To>
			<Credential domain="VendorID">
				<Identity>${header.vendorid}</Identity>
			</Credential>
		</To>
		<Sender>
			<Credential domain="NetworkID">
				<Identity>ReplacedByGroovy</Identity>
			</Credential>
			<UserAgent>S4CORE</UserAgent>
		</Sender>
	</Header>
	<Request deploymentMode="${header.gateway}">
		<StatusUpdateRequest>
			<DocumentReference payloadID="${header.cxml_payloadID}"/>
			<Status code="400" text="${exception.message}">${exception.message}</Status>
			<IntegrationStatus documentStatus="deliveryFailed">
				<IntegrationMessage isSuccessful="no" type="intPackage"/>
			</IntegrationStatus>
		</StatusUpdateRequest>
	</Request>
</cXML>
